of a crowd of people.

806
00:56:01,140 --> 00:56:04,438
And I got hit here
four times by a tiny fist.

807
00:56:04,964 --> 00:56:05,984
Gosh.

808
00:56:06,914 --> 00:56:11,341
Why are you both getting beaten up?
I'm so upset!

809
00:56:17,674 --> 00:56:18,518
Here.

810
00:56:24,113 --> 00:56:26,454
Is that why you're here?

811
00:56:31,645 --> 00:56:33,788
-You can go if you want.
-Who was it?

812
00:56:33,879 --> 00:56:35,050
Want me to beat them up?

813
00:56:36,432 --> 00:56:37,709
Not that.

814
00:56:41,345 --> 00:56:42,375
