martial arts career together.

831
00:58:21,930 --> 00:58:25,003
Let's have fun here and
close the book for good.

832
00:58:25,203 --> 00:58:28,558
You sound like you'll never see me again.

833
00:58:29,043 --> 00:58:31,611
Let's stop seeing each other
as coach and player.

834
00:58:31,811 --> 00:58:32,939
Let's be friends now.

835
00:58:33,428 --> 00:58:35,306
What was that just now?

836
00:58:35,589 --> 00:58:39,137
No. We can't be friends. Let's go.

837
00:58:39,927 --> 00:58:41,466
He's so pig-headed.

838
00:58:56,833 --> 00:58:58,596
What do you think? Isn't it fun?

839
00:58:58,796 --> 00:58:59,837
Isn't it entertaining?

840
00:59:01,984 --> 00:59:03,769
Isn't your heart racing?

841
00:59:03,969 --> 00:59:06,010
Aren't you getting worked up?

842
00:59:06,210 --> 00:59:08,663
When will it end? It's so long.

843
00:59:08,863 --> 00:59:09,858
Fine.

844
00:59:10,645 --> 00:59:11,940
There's one fight left.

845
00:59:12,985 --> 00:59:17,098
The kid coming up dominated
after just two years.

846
00:59:17,298 --> 00:59:19,118
He's got great legs...

847
00:59:20,461 --> 00:59:21,496
Anyway.

848
00:59:23,028 --> 00:59:24,830
Anyway, he does.

849
00:59:28,283 --> 00:59:29,283
Hey.

850
00:59:30,403 --> 00:59:32,371
Just watch. Okay?

851
00:59:32,741 --> 00:59:34,166
Fine.

852
00:59:55,915 --> 00:59:58,573
Now, for the main event.

853
00:59:59,167 --> 01:00:01,359
Here comes Kim Taksu!

854
01:00:05,807 --> 01:00:08,021
In the red corner,

855
01:00:08,221 --> 01:00:10,062
Taksu Kim!

856
01:00:43,577 --> 01:00:46,761
Watch how he's living now.

857
01:00:49,635 --> 01:00:50,962
You did stupid things together.

858
01:00:51,460 --> 01:00:52,599
Why must you hang your head?

859
01:00:57,564 --> 01:00:58,643
Coach.

860
01:01:00,996 --> 01:01:03,078
Why are you being so cruel to me?

861
01:01:30,623 --> 01:01:35,000
